channel.title: Looking for a coder
channel.description:
Hi there, I am part a site, which will remain unknown, and I would like to make a private server for our members. Now, I'm not experienced whatsoever in server making, but my friend and I have worked on a basic source and are looking for an experienced coder to finish the job. My friend will host the server, so you won't have to worry about that. You would also get a moderator spot on the site. All I will say is that it has more than 40k members....
Simply PM me if you're interested.
Thanks for your time.[br][size=1]Posted on: July 13, 2007, 07:35:00 PM[/size][hr]And I forgot to mention, that afterwards, we'd make a website for your server, that looks just like runescape's
